# Liquid Glass Design System

HuiYuYuan uses a glassmorphism dark theme with jade green and gold accents.

## Color palette

| Token | Usage |
|-------|-------|
| `AppColors.jadeGreen` | Primary brand color |
| `AppColors.goldAccent` | Accent, highlight, and trust badges |
| `AppColors.darkBackground` | Page backgrounds |
| `AppColors.glassWhite` | Glass panel overlays |

## Glass panels

```dart
// GOOD: use reusable glass components.
GlassCard(
  child: ...,
)

// BAD: raw one-off glass styling.
Container(
  decoration: BoxDecoration(color: Colors.white.withOpacity(0.1)),
)
```

## Typography

- Title: `Theme.of(context).textTheme.titleLarge`
- Body: `Theme.of(context).textTheme.bodyMedium`
- Avoid bare `Text(..., style: TextStyle(color: Colors.white))`; prefer theme tokens.

## Avoid

- Emojis in UI unless explicitly requested.
- Material default blues such as `Colors.blue`; use `AppColors.*`.
- Hard-coded spacing when `AppSpacing.*` is available.

## New screen checklist

1. Use `Scaffold` with `backgroundColor: AppColors.darkBackground`.
2. Use existing glass components for content areas.
3. Use jade green for primary CTAs and gold for secondary/trust cues.
